        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>Your performance enraptures those who hear it, compelling them to follow you about in admiration. Each creature within the emanation must attempt a Will save when you Cast the Spel} or the first time they enter the area, after which they become temporarily immune for 1 day.</p>\n<p>Once per turn, you can spend a single action, which has the concentrate trait, to increase the emanation's radius by 5 feet. You can @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Dismiss]{Dismiss} the spell.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fascinated]{Fascinated} with you.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature uses all its actions to move toward you and compliment your performance. This effect ends if a hostile action is used against the affected creature.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target gains the minion trait and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Controlled]{Controlled} by you. This effect ends if a hostile action is used against the affected creature, or if you direct the creature to use any action that causes it harm.</p>"
